@DATABASE "The Race"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - T - The Race"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - T
                   ====================================

                                   The Race
                                   ========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Time" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(55541,0)"}           55541,0
@{"Seconds = x  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(55549,255)"}           55549,x (x= 1-255) CHECK!!!!


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         This is for the FULL version of the game
                         only. NOT the playable demo that is on
                         Speccy Sensations 2.


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
